title: John Burnet of Barns: A Romance
author: Buchan, John
snippet: About midday we came to Lanark Moor, where the baggage and shelties, aswell as most of the women and children, were left behind to find anencampment.

title: John Burnet of Barns: A Romance
author: Buchan, John
snippet: Then I rode over Lanark Moor to Hyndford and through the moorof Carmichael and under the great shadow of Tintock.
